@node "Introduction" "Introduction"
@next "Distribution"
@prev "Main"
@{b}Introduction@{ub}

KeepDays is a small deleter for the filecatalogue that can delete
files that are older than a certain date. It can also keep the
physical file, only run on specified sections and in a special
test mode.

@endnode

@node "Distribution" "Distribution"
@next "Responsibility"
@prev "Introduction"
